<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>158</hymn_number>
<title>HLA DAWH A KA SAKTER CH158</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka lungchung ah hladawh ngaingai cu, Jesuh nih nem te'n a sak, Tih
 hlah nangmah sinah ka um ko, Dai tein um tuah, a ti.

[C1]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, Jesuh, Min thlum bik a si; Ka duhnak a tlinter, Kal
   pah hla a ka sakter.

[V2]
 Sualnak nih ka nunnak tingtang hri, A chah i a rawk dih cang, Siseh
 Jesuh nih a peh than ca, Lawmhnak awdawh a um than.

[C2]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, Jesuh, Min thlum bik a si; Ka duhnak a tlinter, Kal
   pah hla a ka sakter.

[V3]
 Amah velngeihnak in ka rum ko, Himnak a thla tang kaa dor, A hmaipanh
 kha ka zoh zungzal i, Lawmhnak hla ka sa lengmang.

[C3]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, Jesuh, Min thlum bik a si; Ka duhnak a tlinter, Kal
   pah hla a ka sakter.

[V4]
 A rauh hlanah a tum than lai i, A sinah a ka hruai lai. Hngalh lo ram
 ah khin kan zuang lai i, Amah he kan uk ti lai.

[C4]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, Jesuh, Min thlum bik a si; Ka duhnak a tlinter, Kal
   pah hla a ka sakter.</lyrics>
</song>